{"tid":2390092,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"（估地方）坐擁710萬住宅中年男聲稱身患絕症 17歲少女即奉上初夜「愛愛」","createTime":"2021-02-01T10:29:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T11:47:57.000Z","uid":84037,"like":9,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"05c3c70bd191e891ae44284bf0b93f77f9607aa2","tid":2390092,"uid":84037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T10:29:26.000Z","msg":"連登日報 （純屬創作，如有雷同，實屬不幸！）<br />\n<br />\n近日網上流傳一篇文章，稱是一名十七歲少女被欺騙感情的自白。該「少女」指，早前於香港著名約炮交友軟件HMD上，認識了一名年約三十的男子。一番網上情話後，兩人互生情愫，但未有作進一步的「踰越」。<br />\n<br />\n該「少女」收到那名男子送予她的禮物。「少女」留意到禮物上的寄出地址，上網翻查後發現該男子原來居住於價值710萬港元的單位。此事以後，少女主動向男方提出「情侶關係」。起初男方猶豫，或許是招架不住熱情如火，青春少艾的女事主，最終答應開展「隔代戀」。期間，男事主稱自己「身患絕症」，會「導致性功能受損」，且壽命「只剩幾年」。該「少女」聽罷，便「自動獻身」。男事主起初拒絕，但最後答應「嘿咻」。<br />\n<br />\n該「少女」於文中聲稱，兩人反目的原因是因為男事主不讓她「去荃灣區範圍」，又指男事主不欲被「屋企人發現」一事令她大感不滿。最終，女事主與男事主對質，男事主將其有家室的事實和盤托出。女事主大為震驚及憤怒，於是把男事主的資料和特徵於網上公開。"},{"pid":"b69a57f6cd850e805368cca44c7be3a6bb90fe5a","tid":2390092,"uid":119729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T10:31:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">把男事主的資料和特徵於網上公開</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76ada704455fcc1db74772e6662caf1a81337418","tid":2390092,"uid":84037,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b69a57f6cd850e805368cca44c7be3a6bb90fe5a","tid":2390092,"uid":119729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T10:31:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">把男事主的資料和特徵於網上公開</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T10:32:55.000Z","msg":"去cctoy 同感情台會搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3875d43ea26e346921060454d2eeb5b521c062","tid":2390092,"uid":84037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T10:47:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d652ec1cd2cfc315035a0ba49ef3a46964a2390a","tid":2390092,"uid":84037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T10:47:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38dcc20c65d826a7994ae18bc33d62ca29a40cbc","tid":2390092,"uid":87155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T10:48:16.000Z","msg":"圖？link?"},{"pid":"9a4c63111f40c2866fc046bf5ec105eff9d99c3a","tid":2390092,"uid":84037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"38dcc20c65d826a7994ae18bc33d62ca29a40cbc","tid":2390092,"uid":87155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T10:48:16.000Z","msg":"圖？link?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T10:50:21.000Z","msg":"［推］31歲無恥梁姓人夫呃17歲學生妹處<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2389283\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2389283</a>"},{"